00:01:31,470 --> 00:01:36,430
[Live in Flame of War]

20
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:40,760
[Episode 22]

21
00:02:34,790 --> 00:02:36,990
When did you come back?

22
00:02:53,130 --> 00:02:56,470
And you're not afraid someone will see.

23
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:58,750
Just let me hug you for a while.

24
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:02,160
Just the way we're doing now.

25
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:08,590
Are you still worrying about Mo Weiyi's matter?

26
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:17,990
I heard that he doesn't want to return to the East Main Camp.

27
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:34,000
Weiyi was brought up by his father since he was a child.

28
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:39,090
Now we haven't figured out the reason for Mo Xibai's death.

29
00:03:39,090 --> 00:03:41,030
Of course, he's not willing to return.

30
00:03:44,530 --> 00:03:46,850
Don't be too worried about it.

31
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:51,940
I believe the truth will be revealed one day.

32
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,280
It will.

33
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:17,900
The governor will visit Beixin next week with the 23th Regiment.

34
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:20,610
They will do military exercises with us for one month.

35
00:04:20,610 --> 00:04:26,180
I'm assuming he will be discussing with me the option of having troops garrison at Suiling after that.

36
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:30,950
What is the governor planning to do?

37
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:34,650
Troops in the South want to go on an expedition to the North.

38
00:04:34,650 --> 00:04:37,760
Expedition to the North? That will make everyone afraid.

39
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:40,930
The two divisions under Yan Laocu are already creating a disturbance.

40
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:45,800
Although they are not attacking in front of our doors yet, we have to be prepared in advance.

41
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:49,530
What if they are? We'll just fight them.

42
00:04:49,530 --> 00:04:52,860
As far as I'm concerned, the governor is being too sensitive.

43
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:55,680
I'm afraid it's not as simple as that.

44
00:04:55,680 --> 00:05:01,100
No matter what, we'll give him a reception at the highest standard.

45
00:05:01,100 --> 00:05:03,660
We'll reinforce the security measures,

46
00:05:03,660 --> 00:05:08,280
and for anything else, we'll just be adaptable.

47
00:05:11,810 --> 00:05:17,530
Commander, the governor is suddenly suggesting a joint garrison by three sides,

48
00:05:17,530 --> 00:05:20,250
and wants to garrison in Suiling.

49
00:05:20,250 --> 00:05:24,260
Is he helping to strengthen the forces of the Ying Army, or is he aiming at something else?

50
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:27,640
I've replied to the governor.

51
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:30,560
He'll send a regiment, and I'll send a regiment, too.

52
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,600
I won't hesitate even just a bit.

53
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:35,910
Are we just sending a regiment to the Beixin City for nothing?

54
00:05:37,670 --> 00:05:41,550
The governor is just taking the chance to eliminate their forces.

55
00:05:42,810 --> 00:05:48,660
You mean... the governor wants to garrison at Suiling in the name of defending again the Northern Expedition,

56
00:05:48,660 --> 00:05:53,810
but in fact, his target is the Ying Army of the Xiao family?

57
00:05:56,570 --> 00:06:02,420
Say, when there's a big show, who will be the happiest?

58
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:04,570
People who watch the show, naturally.

59
00:06:04,570 --> 00:06:07,120
That's why on this matter,

60
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:11,660
we can just be onlookers.

61
00:06:18,790 --> 00:06:20,070
Who sent this?

62
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:22,190
It was Young Third Madam.

63
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:42,420
We are brothers as one, and we will never be apart.

64
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:44,630
Save me!

65
00:06:45,340 --> 00:06:47,960
Anyone here?

66
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:50,190
Save me!

67
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:52,880
Anybody here?

68
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:59,520
Third Brother!

69
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:02,000
Mo Weiyi!

70
00:07:02,650 --> 00:07:05,320
- Mo Weiyi!
- Third Brother!

71
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:07,370
- Mo Weiyi!
- Third Brother!

72
00:07:08,370 --> 00:07:11,160
- Mo Weiyi!
- Mo Weiyi!

73
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:14,510
- Mo Weiyi!
- Third Brother!

74
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:16,050
Are you okay?

75
00:07:16,050 --> 00:07:18,620
I think my leg is broken.

76
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:21,510
It's okay. We'll send you home.

77
00:07:45,810 --> 00:07:50,750
There are ups and downs in one's life, twists and turns in every event.

78
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:56,630
Bosom friends are the most valuable in one's life. How many of them do we really have?

79
00:08:11,730 --> 00:08:13,240
Hello, who is it?

80
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,690
Hello, Miss Fengqi.

81
00:08:15,690 --> 00:08:17,830
Chief Editor Li!

82
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:20,790
Miss Fengqi, thank you so much for your effort.

83
00:08:20,790 --> 00:08:24,760
Lin Tangsheng's book will soon be published again.

84
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:27,350
That's great news.

85
00:08:27,350 --> 00:08:30,470
But... I heard from Minister Zhang

86
00:08:30,470 --> 00:08:34,630
that if we want to publish it again, we need permission from Mr. Lin.

87
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:37,440
He's still in prison.

88
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:39,690
If it's not convenient for you to reach out,

89
00:08:39,690 --> 00:08:42,000
I'll see what I can do.

90
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:45,830
It's okay. We've resolved that problem now.

91
00:08:45,830 --> 00:08:47,910
Oh?

92
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:51,170
You've already contacted him? I thought Governor Cheng said that

93
00:08:51,170 --> 00:08:53,880
no one can contact him.

94
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:55,190
Specifics...

95
00:08:55,190 --> 00:08:57,530
I don't know the specifics of it.

96
00:08:59,070 --> 00:09:02,200
All right. Then that's it for now.

97
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,670
Goodbye.

98
00:09:12,190 --> 00:09:17,790
Lin Hangjing, let's continue to be good friends then.

99
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:31,190
- You're back.
- Yes.

100
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:59,180
It's a normal day. Why did you buy this blush for me?

101
00:09:59,180 --> 00:10:02,450
I heard from Xiao Rong that

102
00:10:02,450 --> 00:10:05,180
you sent a very special gift to Weiyi.

103
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:08,730
The three of you brothers grew up together.

104
00:10:08,730 --> 00:10:10,930
I'm sure he'll come around.

105
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:13,960
Thank you.

106
00:10:15,810 --> 00:10:18,300
This is new on the market. It has the scent of begonias.

107
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:22,090
- Do you like it?
- It smells so good.

108
00:10:22,090 --> 00:10:24,940
- Let me put it on you.
- Wait.

109
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:28,800
Which color do you think will be the prettiest?

110
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:33,660
This... This one?

111
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:39,840
I think every one of the colors looks very nice.

112
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,700
If you put them on your face,

113
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:44,370
there's no color that doesn't look nice.

114
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:49,730
I want to tell you, that sometimes your cheeks have a natural blush.

115
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:52,630
Just like two apples. That's so cute.

116
00:10:57,700 --> 00:10:59,260
Hold it.

117
00:11:22,330 --> 00:11:24,060
Too pretty.

118
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:25,480
Really?

119
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:28,470
You're absolutely stunning.

120
00:11:30,430 --> 00:11:31,820
Let me have a look.

121
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:34,100
It's done! Check it out.

122
00:11:39,010 --> 00:11:42,940
Xiao Beichen! When did you...?

123
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:52,080
Lin Hangjing, why do I like you so much?

124
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,910
[First Society Newspaper]

125
00:12:18,910 --> 00:12:21,020
- Chief Editor.
- Hangjing.

126
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:25,070
This is a sample publication of the articles you published in the past three months.

127
00:12:25,070 --> 00:12:28,530
I've cleaned it up for you. You can have it.

128
00:12:28,530 --> 00:12:30,980
Thank you, Chief Editor.

129
00:12:30,980 --> 00:12:35,470
I asked you to come here to share some good news with you.

130
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:40,380
Look.

131
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:47,200
They've lifted the ban on the economy book your father wrote.

132
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:49,460
Now we can publish it.

133
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:52,150
Ever since my father was imprisoned by Governor Cheng,

134
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:56,470
his book was decided to be a banned book.

135
00:12:56,470 --> 00:13:00,970
Every time my father mentioned it in the letter, he thought it was a huge regret.

136
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:05,160
If he were to know about it, he'd definitely be happy.

137
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:09,150
Thanks to the movie star, Miss Zheng Fengqi.

138
00:13:09,150 --> 00:13:13,280
I heard that she's been negotiating this using her network with the Ministry of Culture of the Central Government.

139
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:16,530
So your father's work can be brought to light again.

140
00:13:16,530 --> 00:13:18,820
Fengqi?

141
00:13:29,410 --> 00:13:33,430
Third Brother, I have some good news to share.

142
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:37,460
My father's book is being published again.

143
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:43,230
This time, it's all thanks to Fengqi.

144
00:13:43,230 --> 00:13:47,110
Do you know? Ever since my father's term of imprisonment has been changed,

145
00:13:47,110 --> 00:13:51,160
I've been counting the days, anticipating his return.

146
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,810
And when he gets out of prison

147
00:13:53,810 --> 00:13:57,850
and sees his book published again, he will be very happy.

148
00:14:05,690 --> 00:14:07,120
Okay.

149
00:14:10,540 --> 00:14:12,100
Sleep.

150
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:19,030
Here.

151
00:14:28,650 --> 00:14:32,380
Hangjing, I'm sorry.

152
00:14:37,730 --> 00:14:41,530
[Welcome Banquet for Governor Jin's Arrival in Beixin]

153
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:55,290
This time, Governor Jin

154
00:14:55,290 --> 00:14:58,370
is visiting Beixin, and everyone places much importance on it.

155
00:14:58,370 --> 00:15:01,890
Let us know if there's anything we can do, Seventh Madam.

156
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:06,400
Third Master and his wife are here!

157
00:15:07,010 --> 00:15:10,180
Beichen! Hangjing! Come over here!

158
00:15:11,130 --> 00:15:13,140
Seventh Aunt.

159
00:15:13,140 --> 00:15:16,230
- Seventh Aunt.
- We've been waiting for you two for such a long time.

160
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:37,340
- Excuse me for a second.
- Okay.

161
00:15:39,130 --> 00:15:41,460
- Fengqi.
- Father.

162
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:42,940
Come with me.

163
00:15:46,380 --> 00:15:49,310
Daughter, what brings you here?

164
00:15:49,310 --> 00:15:52,190
Hangjing and Third Brother invited me.

165
00:15:52,190 --> 00:15:55,090
How can I refuse their invitation?

166
00:15:58,510 --> 00:16:02,250
Father, don't worry about me.

167
00:16:02,250 --> 00:16:04,820
- I...
- Governor Jin is here!

168
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:30,930
- Beichen! Congratulations.
- Governor.

169
00:16:30,930 --> 00:16:34,000
You've been promoted as the Deputy Commander of the Ying Army.

170
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:37,090
And you're the youngest deputy commander in the three armies.

171
00:16:37,090 --> 00:16:40,860
I'm not talented. I look forward to receiving your guidance in the future.

172
00:16:40,860 --> 00:16:44,720
You're young and have a promising future. You're the hope of older generations like us.

173
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,910
Thank you, Governor.

174
00:16:45,910 --> 00:16:50,110
Let me introduce her to you. This is my daughter, Rouke.

175
00:16:50,110 --> 00:16:52,340
You'd met her when you were much younger.

176
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:55,020
Now, do you still recognize each other?

177
00:16:55,020 --> 00:16:59,180
Yes, we were only fifteen when we met. It's been a long time.

178
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:01,610
Nice to meet you again, Miss Rouke.

179
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:05,310
Is this Third Master's wife?

180
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:07,110
Miss Rouke.

181
00:17:07,110 --> 00:17:10,830
I've heard that Third Master's wife was beautiful, talented, and elegant.

182
00:17:10,830 --> 00:17:13,350
Now I get to meet you in person and those words are true.

183
00:17:13,350 --> 00:17:15,860
Thank you for your compliment, Miss Rouke.

184
00:17:15,860 --> 00:17:19,790
Let me introduce one more person. Mu Zizheng.

185
00:17:19,790 --> 00:17:22,290
This is my new foster son.

186
00:17:23,050 --> 00:17:25,750
He's the Head of Administration at the camp of the Governor's Office.

187
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:28,820
He's in charge of training soldiers.

188
00:17:28,820 --> 00:17:30,680
Mu Zizheng?

189
00:17:31,300 --> 00:17:36,150
Zizheng, meet with Third Master Xiao and his wife.

190
00:17:37,350 --> 00:17:39,030
Nice to meet you.

191
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:43,300
Sir Mu.

192
00:17:46,370 --> 00:17:48,930
Sir Mu must be extremely talented

193
00:17:48,930 --> 00:17:50,900
to be Governor Jin's foster son.

194
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:52,270
Thank you for your compliment, Third Master.

195
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:56,230
I've long heard of your reputation.

196
00:17:56,230 --> 00:17:59,170
All right. It's a wonderful night.

197
00:17:59,170 --> 00:18:00,400
Everybody!

198
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:03,890
Dance and drink! Help yourselves!

199
00:18:03,890 --> 00:18:06,660
Thank you, Governor!

200
00:18:32,540 --> 00:18:35,110
I heard that the Northern Expeditionary Army

201
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:37,690
has assembled in Shaoguan.

202
00:18:37,690 --> 00:18:41,770
I think it's quite crucial for us to build up a defense in Yaochong.

203
00:18:41,770 --> 00:18:45,120
This time, we're uniting three sides

204
00:18:45,120 --> 00:18:47,580
to garrison.

205
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:53,020
I've already asked Jingxiong to lead troops there first.

206
00:18:54,090 --> 00:18:55,580
I’ll lead the 23rd Regiment.

207
00:18:55,580 --> 00:18:58,840
And we'll practice joint military exercises with the East Main Camp together for a month.

208
00:18:58,840 --> 00:19:00,760
When they're ready to fight together,

209
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:03,510
we'll move our troops to Suiling together.

210
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:06,970
Beichen, what do you think?

211
00:19:06,970 --> 00:19:09,270
Beichen will definitely cooperate as much as I can.

212
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:12,910
I look forward to the outcome of this joint military exercise.

213
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:17,950
Everyone, we should congratulate the promotion

214
00:19:17,950 --> 00:19:19,890
of Deputy Commander Xiao. Come!

215
00:19:19,890 --> 00:19:22,260
Congratulations on your promotion, Deputy Commander Xiao.

216
00:19:22,260 --> 00:19:24,090
Thank you, everyone.

217
00:19:27,210 --> 00:19:28,900
Isn't my Third Master handsome?

218
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,170
Of course!

219
00:19:30,170 --> 00:19:31,880
Yeah, they're a perfect match.

220
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:35,980
He became Deputy Commander at such a young age. What an achievement!

221
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:38,360
Hangjing, don't you think so?

222
00:19:40,610 --> 00:19:43,180
Seventh Aunt, please excuse me for a moment.

223
00:19:43,180 --> 00:19:44,890
Sure.

224
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:02,680
Governor, can you excuse me for a moment?

225
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:04,400
Please.

226
00:20:05,990 --> 00:20:09,860
Beichen, can I ask you for a dance?

227
00:20:11,410 --> 00:20:14,420
Beichen, you should be the host tonight.

228
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:17,420
Please bring Rouke to a dance.

229
00:20:19,420 --> 00:20:21,190
Miss Rouke.

230
00:20:46,390 --> 00:20:50,710
[Restroom]

231
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:56,680
Zizheng, let go of me first!

232
00:21:01,660 --> 00:21:03,820
Hangjing.

233
00:21:03,820 --> 00:21:05,920
Why did you marry Xiao Beichen?

234
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:08,110
Why did you marry someone you don't love?

235
00:21:08,110 --> 00:21:11,890
Zizheng, it's a long story. Tell me first...

236
00:21:11,890 --> 00:21:15,040
Where did you go that day without saying goodbye?

237
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:17,940
And why did you become Governor Jin's foster son?

238
00:21:17,940 --> 00:21:22,110
Do you remember when you asked me why I tried to assassinate Kang Jingxiong?

239
00:21:23,690 --> 00:21:26,480
I joined the Youth Society very early on.

240
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:28,130
Youth Society?

241
00:21:28,130 --> 00:21:30,010
Correct.

242
00:21:30,010 --> 00:21:32,240
When?

243
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:36,660
Three years ago. When we were at a student rally,

244
00:21:36,660 --> 00:21:39,750
the executive of Beixin Youth Association, Ding Rouyong, found me

245
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:41,690
and wished for me to join them.

246
00:21:41,690 --> 00:21:45,070
Since then, he secretly trained me for half a year.

247
00:21:46,070 --> 00:21:50,560
That's why you rarely showed up in the newspaper office for a period of time.

248
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:53,480
One day before we were about to take the ship to the south,

249
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:55,410
the organization gave me an urgent task.

250
00:21:55,410 --> 00:21:59,390
I had to leave immediately. I had no time to explain it to you.

251
00:21:59,390 --> 00:22:01,650
So I had Brother Yong...

252
00:22:03,210 --> 00:22:07,090
but he didn't give the letter to you.

253
00:22:07,090 --> 00:22:12,790
Then I was sent to a labor camp. It was impossible for me to get in contact with the outside world there.

254
00:22:12,790 --> 00:22:15,760
Then a lot of things happened.

255
00:22:15,760 --> 00:22:19,030
Now I've become the foster son of Jin Cheng.

256
00:22:19,030 --> 00:22:21,200
After that,

257
00:22:21,830 --> 00:22:24,080
I will tell you all about it in the future slowly.

258
00:22:24,080 --> 00:22:26,100
You know what has happened now.

259
00:22:26,100 --> 00:22:31,130
Then you tell me now how Xiao Beichen forced you to marry him.

260
00:22:31,130 --> 00:22:34,010
Zizheng, it's not like what you think.

261
00:22:34,010 --> 00:22:36,760
What is it like, then?

262
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:41,220
Hangjing, you don't need to be afraid of Xiao Beichen. I'm protected by the Governor and Sister Rouke.

263
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:44,290
She sees me as her biological brother. She will help us.

264
00:22:44,290 --> 00:22:46,630
Zizheng.

265
00:22:46,630 --> 00:22:49,270
No one forced me.

266
00:22:49,270 --> 00:22:51,940
I married him willingly.

267
00:22:57,050 --> 00:22:59,060
What are you saying?

268
00:23:05,090 --> 00:23:08,260
That's impossible. Hangjing, you can tell me the truth.

269
00:23:08,260 --> 00:23:12,370
Have you forgotten the days we were true to each other? Was that all fake?

270
00:23:12,370 --> 00:23:15,490
You surely know how I feel about you.

271
00:23:15,490 --> 00:23:19,080
You cared about me. You looked after me.

272
00:23:19,080 --> 00:23:22,290
I know it. It's because you're blaming me for leaving without notice.

273
00:23:22,290 --> 00:23:26,290
I apologize to you. I can do anything to make it up to you.

274
00:23:26,290 --> 00:23:28,680
Zizheng, calm down.

275
00:23:29,490 --> 00:23:33,050
A lot of things have happened while you were gone.

276
00:23:33,050 --> 00:23:36,490
But seeing that you are safe, I am at ease.

277
00:23:39,170 --> 00:23:43,200
I have been gone for quite a while. I need to go now.

278
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:48,340
What would you think if I told you that my leaving Beixin was Xiao Beichen's doing?

279
00:23:51,460 --> 00:23:53,740
What did you say?

280
00:23:53,740 --> 00:23:55,380
You won't believe it, right?

281
00:23:55,380 --> 00:23:58,270
You said it was a mission given to you by the Youth Union.

282
00:23:58,270 --> 00:24:00,310
Yes.

283
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:03,840
But Xiao Beichen plotted it.

284
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:08,650
He knew who I was when I was trying to kill Kang Jingxiong.

285
00:24:08,650 --> 00:24:12,790
He sent people to keep an eye on me and the members of the Youth Union.

286
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:17,930
He knew that we had bought tickets to go to the south to save your father.

287
00:24:17,930 --> 00:24:20,930
In order to separate us, he found Brother Yong.

288
00:24:20,930 --> 00:24:25,770
He threatened Brother Yong with my life.

289
00:24:27,210 --> 00:24:29,030
I don't believe it.

290
00:24:31,610 --> 00:24:33,950
No, I don't believe it.

291
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:39,170
Hangjing, Xiao Beichen isn't as simple as you think.

292
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:59,580
Sir Mu, I see you're chatting with my wife.

293
00:25:00,980 --> 00:25:02,510
Yes.

294
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:09,080
I don't know why I get along well with Third Young Madam.

295
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:12,260
Hangjing.

296
00:25:14,570 --> 00:25:16,130
Let's go.

297
00:25:27,420 --> 00:25:29,670
There you are.

298
00:25:31,580 --> 00:25:36,610
Hangjing, there are some Madams and Misses that I don't know. Can you introduce me to them?

299
00:25:36,610 --> 00:25:38,510
Of course I can.

300
00:25:49,080 --> 00:25:51,640
I thought you left.

301
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:53,680
How come you're back?

302
00:25:54,900 --> 00:25:59,710
You should know why I left.

303
00:25:59,710 --> 00:26:02,100
You want to steal Hangjing from me?

304
00:26:03,020 --> 00:26:05,360
Are you scared?

305
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:09,340
Hangjing is my lawful wife.

306
00:26:09,340 --> 00:26:13,200
My Madam. I'm scared?

307
00:26:14,630 --> 00:26:16,490
Xiao Beichen,

308
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:22,370
I don't care what despicable means you used to force Hangjing to marry you.

309
00:26:22,370 --> 00:26:25,910
I will have her return to my side.

310
00:26:25,910 --> 00:26:30,530
This time, I will make sure you see clearly that

311
00:26:30,530 --> 00:26:34,890
the person Hangjing truly loves is me.

312
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:40,150
Okay. You can try.

313
00:27:14,430 --> 00:27:17,460
You can ask me anything you want to ask.

314
00:27:17,460 --> 00:27:18,980
I have nothing to ask about.

315
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:30,440
Mu Zizheng told you I made him leave Beixin, didn't he?

316
00:27:43,930 --> 00:27:46,540
If there was another opportunity,

317
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:50,280
I would still do the same.

318
00:27:51,730 --> 00:27:54,670
So you admit it?

319
00:27:54,670 --> 00:27:59,460
Lin Hangjing, people are selfish when it comes to love.

320
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:04,700
I didn't threaten him with a gun on his head. He chose to leave himself.

321
00:28:04,700 --> 00:28:09,010
Did you really think going to the south with him

322
00:28:09,010 --> 00:28:11,320
would really save your father's life?

323
00:28:11,320 --> 00:28:14,980
So, you made the decision for me?

324
00:28:14,980 --> 00:28:18,450
Do you know you almost got him killed?

325
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:36,700
Look at you.

326
00:28:36,700 --> 00:28:40,720
You lost your reasoning as soon after you knew he was back.

327
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:58,480
[Cheng Jing Girls School]

328
00:28:58,480 --> 00:29:02,440
Good morning.

329
00:29:03,490 --> 00:29:07,660
Hangjing, there's a letter for you. It was just delivered to the school.

330
00:29:13,110 --> 00:29:16,590
[See you at the old place at 1:00 p.m. today. From, Zizheng.]

331
00:29:22,520 --> 00:29:27,520
Hangjing, what happened? Are you okay?

332
00:29:27,520 --> 00:29:29,030
I'm fine.

333
00:29:35,460 --> 00:29:39,330
[Equip your mind to think fairly and do right.]

334
00:30:05,420 --> 00:30:09,790
Zizheng, you've been here for hours.

335
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:27,400
Zizheng, perhaps Hangjing was delayed by something.

336
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:29,900
How about we go back first?

337
00:30:33,060 --> 00:30:34,930
I want to wait a bit more.

338
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:41,510
All right then. I will stay here with you.

339
00:31:43,860 --> 00:31:45,870
March!

340
00:31:47,650 --> 00:31:49,610
[Military Rules are Unbreakable]

341
00:32:02,190 --> 00:32:04,150
Stand at attention!

342
00:32:06,340 --> 00:32:10,190
Report in! All rallied up!

343
00:32:11,500 --> 00:32:16,040
Good. You guys are well-trained. I'm impressed.

344
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:18,500
Thank you for your compliment, Governor.

345
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:22,570
My father always said that even the best troops need training.

346
00:32:22,570 --> 00:32:24,900
They are the protectors of the land.

347
00:32:24,900 --> 00:32:30,180
Your father is right. Good generals and soldiers are the foundation of an army.

348
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:33,940
Your father taught you well, and you have done it well.

349
00:32:38,310 --> 00:32:41,060
Where is the 33rd Regiment?

350
00:32:41,060 --> 00:32:44,240
On this visit, I brought

351
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:46,850
the 32nd Regiment which is the Spike Regiment.

352
00:32:46,850 --> 00:32:52,560
I heard your Tiger Regiment is an invincible troop.

353
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:55,840
Since we're having a military exercise,

354
00:32:55,840 --> 00:32:59,170
I think we should see how the two troops fight against each other.

355
00:32:59,170 --> 00:33:00,950
I'm flattered, Governor.

356
00:33:00,950 --> 00:33:05,680
They're no match to your Spike Regiment.

357
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:10,160
I'm worried they stand no chance in front of your troops.

358
00:33:11,100 --> 00:33:15,090
Is the Tiger Regiment Third Master Xiao's secret weapon

359
00:33:15,090 --> 00:33:17,800
so you don't bear to let us see it?

360
00:33:28,030 --> 00:33:30,200
Zizheng.

361
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:32,680
Third Master Xiao, please don’t mind me.

362
00:33:33,440 --> 00:33:36,860
Sir Mu, you really know how to tell jokes.

363
00:33:36,860 --> 00:33:40,780
The entire Ying Army has the best soldiers who serve the governor.

364
00:33:40,780 --> 00:33:44,550
If you put it that way, let’s see the true ability on the battlefield.

365
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:46,400
Let’s start.

366
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:48,010
Start the foot drill.

367
00:34:39,160 --> 00:34:42,140
[Military Rules are Unbreakable]

368
00:34:45,110 --> 00:34:48,100
Foster-father, now that we see it with our own eyes,

369
00:34:48,100 --> 00:34:52,550
I admire Third Master Xiao’s Tiger Regiment.

370
00:34:52,550 --> 00:34:56,630
You have indeed learned a lot of things during this trip.

371
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:58,580
Yes. It seems like

372
00:34:58,580 --> 00:35:04,640
I need to learn from Third Master Xiao from now on.

373
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:09,550
Sir Mu, you’re too kind. I’m here for you.

374
00:35:13,720 --> 00:35:16,370
[Hot Springs Villa]

375
00:35:19,750 --> 00:35:22,000
After today’s military exercises,

376
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:25,640
what do you think about Xiao Beichen’s troops?

377
00:35:30,550 --> 00:35:33,440
The Ying Army enforces strict orders and follows the rules,

378
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:36,760
I must say it’s very good.

379
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:39,470
Especially Xiao Beichen’s Tiger Regiment.

380
00:35:39,470 --> 00:35:42,340
They are fierce; one of them can go against ten.

381
00:35:42,340 --> 00:35:45,670
I have to say, Xiao Beichen knows how to rule his army.

382
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:47,850
Continue speaking.

383
00:35:47,850 --> 00:35:50,730
This is how I see him.

384
00:35:50,730 --> 00:35:54,390
Although you can gain profits from him,

385
00:35:54,390 --> 00:35:58,790
he can also be our biggest threat.

386
00:35:58,790 --> 00:36:00,710
If he can't be used by you,

387
00:36:00,710 --> 00:36:04,040
before he becomes stronger,

388
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:06,540
it’s better to dampen his spirit.

389
00:36:08,100 --> 00:36:11,430
You know how to use people and point out their strengths and shortfalls.

390
00:36:11,430 --> 00:36:15,670
So, Zizheng, your observation is very objective.

391
00:36:15,670 --> 00:36:20,190
So, Foster-father, what are you planning to do next?

392
00:36:20,190 --> 00:36:24,160
I want to know if Xiao Beichen pretends to be sincere,

393
00:36:24,160 --> 00:36:26,280
or if he is loyal.

394
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:31,000
We need to take away his best troops in order to know.

395
00:36:33,140 --> 00:36:36,760
You want to redeploy the Tiger Regiment?

396
00:36:37,810 --> 00:36:40,560
Military exercises are about to start.

397
00:36:40,560 --> 00:36:43,020
Stay put and don’t act rashly.

398
00:36:43,020 --> 00:36:44,680
Yes.

399
00:37:00,990 --> 00:37:03,630
Hangjing, what are you reading?

400
00:37:04,430 --> 00:37:08,820
The Beixin Orphanage accepted a new group of children, this is the list with the names.

401
00:37:08,820 --> 00:37:10,670
They’re all battlefield orphans?

402
00:37:10,670 --> 00:37:14,660
Yes. This group of children's situation

403
00:37:14,660 --> 00:37:17,710
is a bit more different compared to the others in the past.

404
00:37:17,710 --> 00:37:20,810
A lot of them have mental trauma.

405
00:37:20,810 --> 00:37:24,490
Some even saw their parents die in front of their eyes.

406
00:37:24,490 --> 00:37:28,650
That’s too pitiful. You’ll need more helping hands then.

407
00:37:28,650 --> 00:37:32,530
That’s right. I need more help and donations.

408
00:37:32,530 --> 00:37:35,570
Jiade Auction House in Chengdong reached out to Director Zhang.

409
00:37:35,570 --> 00:37:38,990
They wanted to host a charity auction for the kids.

410
00:37:38,990 --> 00:37:42,820
Even an auction house would do this act? They have the heart of Buddhavista.

411
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:46,230
You have event planning experience, can you help me out?

412
00:37:46,230 --> 00:37:48,680
Of course.

413
00:37:48,680 --> 00:37:52,180
How about this? I’ll gather a group of female students to help.

414
00:37:52,180 --> 00:37:56,480
They can send out flyers or something. It would be something they could do for these kids.

415
00:37:56,480 --> 00:38:00,490
That’s great. More people, more power.

416
00:38:00,490 --> 00:38:03,700
Hangjing, there's a Miss Jin here for you.

417
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:09,000
Miss Jin?

418
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:11,870
Can you spare me some time?

419
00:38:11,870 --> 00:38:15,760
I’m sorry, I still have classes later.

420
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:18,130
I won’t use too much of your time.

421
00:38:18,130 --> 00:38:21,980
There are just some matters you need to know.

422
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:26,700
[Office]

423
00:38:31,870 --> 00:38:34,260
How could that be?

424
00:38:34,260 --> 00:38:39,730
I didn’t know Zizheng had gone through so much during this time.

425
00:38:39,730 --> 00:38:42,600
He doesn’t want to tell you anything sad.

426
00:38:42,600 --> 00:38:46,610
I don’t know well what had happened to him prior.

427
00:38:46,610 --> 00:38:49,900
But when I found him outside the border in the mountain,

428
00:38:49,900 --> 00:38:54,220
he had injury wounds and his body was barely covered.

429
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:58,190
I don’t know how many days he had been in hunger and under the cold temperature.

430
00:38:58,190 --> 00:39:02,410
He was at the blink of death, no different from a corpse.

431
00:39:06,450 --> 00:39:11,090
His wounds were mostly festered.

432
00:39:11,090 --> 00:39:14,030
The doctor had already given up.

433
00:39:14,030 --> 00:39:18,090
But in order to live,

434
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:23,540
he cut off his rotted flesh without any anesthesia.

435
00:39:23,540 --> 00:39:26,910
While he was in his last breath,

436
00:39:26,910 --> 00:39:29,720
he was crying for one person’s name.

437
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:33,690
“Hangjing."

438
00:39:40,020 --> 00:39:44,150
I didn't come here today to try to intervene in your choice,

439
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:46,740
I just wanted to tell you that

440
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:49,770
you’re everything to him.

441
00:39:49,770 --> 00:39:53,560
I hope no matter what kind of thoughts you have with him,

442
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:56,540
you can clarify with him face to face.

443
00:39:56,540 --> 00:40:00,050
I don’t want him to have any regrets.

444
00:40:23,940 --> 00:40:25,600
You’re here.

445
00:40:39,430 --> 00:40:42,950
I miss my time working at the kite store.

446
00:40:42,950 --> 00:40:47,600
Back then, you came to help me when you had time.

447
00:40:48,220 --> 00:40:53,120
I was in charge of the forms, and you were responsible for coloring.

448
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:58,480
The kites we made together sold particularly well.

449
00:40:58,480 --> 00:41:02,370
Later, you introduced me to work at the newspaper.

450
00:41:03,170 --> 00:41:06,610
You wrote articles and I took pictures.

451
00:41:07,710 --> 00:41:12,480
We pointed out the social injustice and punished the evil.

452
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:14,720
We helped the weak.

453
00:41:14,720 --> 00:41:19,490
I thought we were the best partners.

454
00:41:22,390 --> 00:41:26,740
I thought from time to time,

455
00:41:26,740 --> 00:41:31,680
"Is it possible to have all these coincidences in this vast world?"

456
00:41:33,020 --> 00:41:36,170
I took a few pictures at the orphanage for the press,

457
00:41:36,170 --> 00:41:40,040
and you happened to be the writer of the article.

458
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:45,960
I considered this... fate.

459
00:41:54,370 --> 00:41:57,410
Hangjing, do you still remember

460
00:41:57,410 --> 00:42:02,340
